
| Feature               | Compiler                                         | Interpreter                         |
| --------------------- | ------------------------------------------------ | ----------------------------------- |
| **Definition**        | Converts whole program into machine code at once | Converts and runs code line by line |
| **Execution**         | After compilation, program runs directly         | Executes immediately line-by-line   |
| **Speed**             | Faster (after compilation) 🚀                    | Slower (checks each line) 🐢        |
| **Error Checking**    | Shows all errors after compilation               | Shows errors one by one             |
| **Output**            | Generates an executable file (.exe)              | No separate file generated          |
| **Example Languages** | C, C++                                           | Python, JavaScript                  ो

### 🧠 Compiler

* पूरा code पहले compile होता है
* अगर 10 errors हैं → सब एक साथ दिखेंगे
* फिर program run होगा

### 🧠 Interpreter

* Code line by line चलता है
* जहाँ error आएगा → वहीं रुक जाएगा
